                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Uncertainty in the normalization of the",
                "experiment as given in Table I:",
                "Contributions to the positron detection efficiency and",
                "its uncertainty",
                "1. Positron spectrum cutoff-0.92+-3%,",
                "2. Annihilation in Flight-0.93+-3%,",
                "3. Cerenkov counter Efficiencies-0.97+3%(-5%),",
                "4. Extended size of positron source- 1.00+-2%,",
                "5. Solid angle uncertainty-1.00+-4%,",
                "6. Veto counter false rejection-0.99+1%-3%,",
                "7. Positron multiple scattering in counters-0.97+-2%,",
                "8. Holes at 0-degree and 180-degree- negligible",
                "effect,",
                "9. Shadowing by target assembly- negligible effect,",
                "10. Positive muon-positron directional correlation-",
                "negligible effect,",
                "11. Positive pion Interaction before decay- negligible",
